Homepage: https://github.com/shadow1ng/fscan
Description: Intranet penetration test tool for scanning vulnerabilities
 fscan is a comprehensive intranet security scanning tool that
 performs port scanning, web fingerprinting, weak password detection,
 and vulnerability exploitation in internal network environments.
